products.name: Stivale Elastico Uomo
products.description:
Casual and chic boot at the same time. Practical when worn thanks to the lateral elastic bands, this does not detract from the elegance of the model thanks to the specially chosen parade shape. The manually milled rubber sole with midsole guarantees waterproofness and thermal insulation, light and flexible in equal measure.
• Upper: vegetable tanned calfskin
• Sole: Vibram rubber with rubber midsole, leather heel, rubber heel
